-- python install mac
download latest python
right click pkg file to start Python Installer, follow the instruction
phthon will be installed in Applications directory, /Applications/Python 3.9
double click Install Certification icon in the Finder window to install certification (required)
type python to verify version
python --version
PATH=/bin:/usr/bin:/usr/local/bin:${PATH}
export PATH

